Privacy Policy
This privacy policy applies when using the application
Finances
on iOS and macOS.
Collection of Information
You provide information by adding and managing transactions, accounts and journals. This information is stored on the device.
Use of Information
The collected information is only used for bookkeeping services.
Sharing of Information
The collected information is neither shared with any third-party entity nor stored on servers other than iCloud servers, which are operated by Apple.
